.ready(function () {\t\n\t\twx.hideOptionMenu();\n\t});\n\n\u003c/script\u003e\n....\n```\n\n**Platform(s) Affected:**\n- coupon.ec-starbucks.cn(Starbucks East China in using)\n\n## Steps To Reproduce:\n\n#### plan A(easy)\n1. request the endpoint I offer\n2. you will find the reponse contain \"weixin.spcc.mobi\"\n3. visit the **weixin.spcc.mobi** you will find that this domain is on sale\n\n#### plan B(complicated)\n1. register a wechat account(download the app(name is wechat) from app store or play store)\n2. search wechat offical account **星巴克江浙沪** then follow\n3. click my card\n4. you can find the requests as the I had mention.\n\n## Recommendations for fix\nremove the the unused **weixin.spcc.mobi** endpoint\n\n## Impact\n\nthe domain is on sale, if attacker buy  this domain, can full control this domain for(Phishing Attack and etc.)","weakness":{"id":26,"name":"Improper Access Control - Generic"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":396033,"file_name":"burp_request.jpg","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/000/396/033/7418b9367c75fcc5a4d8af7b08c2e59e849458a7/burp_request.jpg?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22burp_request.jpg%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27burp_request.jpg\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fjpeg\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQSCAY3YES%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T093833Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECkaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIQCZVfPyc2Ro5pKvfyjPMi0kEG8XbLQUtSUmeXikKx%2FnIwIgLsKc8gWaLHpc9AYiDm3LeD1cXQyDRxxDT7K5pbEJCmwqugUI8v%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FARADGgwwMTM2MTkyNzQ4NDkiDCrezpwQ3rBCmJxmtCqOBa7CklRX%2FTd8isAhpszBYTMuEOWSAoHuI7wy9BVRNQxHuP9%2BSRSEt%2BZGLxF4Z4PGFk3wtEROcuTjDAh6mzL1GL1SfbskNqgkxjCh3BVVB%2BTpHNaUToCodEEZTSlw7hwEINo3SHh%2Fl55qwILARbpWO1vFjepZWw2nSJb4ha3U6%2B0SOHvlN8xbW667QznhfEiCh8Dqb9H1LzSeCc4Qy